[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m125[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m126[0m[39m:        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb.length < PFB_[0m[1;33mHEAD[0m[39mER_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m127[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m128[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB header missing"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m129[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m130[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m read into segments and keep them[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:133[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m137[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m133[0m[39m:        ByteArrayInputStream in = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m134[0m[39m:        int total = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m135[0m[39m:        do[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m136[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:            int r = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Issue Analysis and Root Cause  [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:103[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m107[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m calls [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, eagerly loading the entire InputStream into memory without any[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize bound. This allows a malicious or malformed PFB font stream larger than [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mavailable heap to blow out memory before any of the existing `MAX_LENGTH` [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msafeguards in `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` ever run.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The downstream font-loading layers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDType1Font, PDFontFactory, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m simply [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpass the embedded font bytes via `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and only catch [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException`, so guarding that constructor is the correct mitigation point.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Core Fix: Bounded Read of InputStream  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Replace the unbounded `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call with a streaming read that [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforces the same `MAX_LENGTH` [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m limit already used in `parsePfb`.  [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Implement a private helper method [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream, int [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that reads the input in chunks [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m KiB at a time[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, accumulates [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minto a `ByteArrayOutputStream`, tracks the total bytes read, and throws an [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` if the total would exceed `MAX_LENGTH`.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor, invoke this helper to obtain the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfont data byte array, then call `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` as before.  [0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Detailed Patch Steps  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   a[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m In `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`, add a [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static helper method near the top of the class:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m buffer = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m8192[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long totalRead = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         int n;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mn = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             totalRead += n;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotalRead > maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB font exceeds maximum allowed size: "[0m[39m + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotalRead[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mbaos.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;35mbaos.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   b[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Modify the constructor:[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Read at most MAX_LENGTH bytes to prevent uncontrolled heap usage[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   c[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Remove or comment out the original `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;` line.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The existing `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, including its header checks and [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mper-segment `MAX_LENGTH` summation, remains unchanged.  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The overall maximum memory footprint for PFB parsing stays consistent [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfor the initial buffer + per-segment check up to [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Downstream callers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDType1Font, PDFontFactory[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m still catch `IOException`, so [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed or oversize PFB data will be logged as a damaged font but will not crash [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe JVM.[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification and Side-Effect Mitigation  [0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By bounding the initial read, we guard against heap exhaustion without [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39maltering any external or fuzzing harness logic.  [0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance impact is minimal: the helper reads in small fixed-size chunks [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m8[0m[39m [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mKiB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, which is comparable to typical IO buffering.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing tests for valid PFB fonts [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwell under [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will continue to pass [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout modification.  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No external libraries or harness code are touched; tests and fuzzers will [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger an `IOException` instead of an `OutOfMemoryError`, leading to the correct [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m“damaged font” fallback path.[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Optional Further Enhancement  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In a future major version, consider refactoring `parsePfb` to accept an [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`InputStream` directly, eliminating the need for any full-byte-array buffering and [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menabling on-the-fly streaming parse with the same size checks. For now, the [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbounded-read helper achieves the security fix with minimal code changes.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m)[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mDEDUP_TOKEN: 4fc18e0e0662428e[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m== libFuzzer crashing input ==[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m===Evaluation [0m[33mReport[0m[39m===[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe project’s PDF parsing component [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m was [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcrashing under fuzzing due to an unbounded read of a PFB font stream, leading to an[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mOutOfMemoryError. To mitigate this, a patch was proposed that:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Introduced a new helper method `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` which[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreads the input in chunks and enforces an upper bound on the total bytes read.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Replaced the original `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call in the `PfbParser` constructor [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the build failed in the FontBox module with a compilation[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39merror:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mincompatible types: possible lossy conversion from long to int[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis indicates a mismatch between the type of `MAX_LENGTH` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpresumably a `long`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the `int` parameter expected by `readLimited`.[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A fuzzer run triggered a `FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of memory` exception.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The root Java exception was `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurring in `[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace excerpt:[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     at [0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[1;39m)[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     at org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.<init>[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:116[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[33m...[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     at [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mcom.example.PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPDFExtractTextFuzzer.jav[0m[1;92ma:41[0m[1;39m)[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Observation: the parser reads the entire PFB font into a byte array [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, allowing unbounded memory growth.[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A new private static method `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` was [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madded.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - It reads from the stream in [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m KB buffers.  [0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - It tracks `totalRead` as a `long`.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - If `totalRead` exceeds `maxLength`, it throws an `IOException`.  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor, the code was changed from:[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     to[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The intention was to cap the amount of memory used when loading PFB data.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch Result  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - During Maven compilation of the FontBox module, the following error occurred:[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     incompatible types: possible lossy conversion from long to int[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This error points at the call site for `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating that `MAX_LENGTH` is defined as a `long`, while `readLimited` expects an[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`int` for `maxLength`.[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The declaration of `MAX_LENGTH` in `PfbParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcheck its type and intended [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munit[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The signature of the new `readLimited` method [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconsider accepting a `long` or [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmatching the type of `MAX_LENGTH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Other parts of `PfbParser`, especially the `parsePfb` method and how it [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minterprets section lengths, to ensure consistency with any size checks.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Any other code in FontBox or PDFBox that reads large streams into memory [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithout bounds [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., other font formats or content stream operators[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m195[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m196[0m[39m:                cleartomarkSegment = ar;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m197[0m[39m:                continue;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m198[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m199[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mSystem.arraycopy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, pfbdata, dstPos, ar.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m200[0m[39m:            dstPos += ar.length;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:63[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m75[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:     * the EOF marker.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:    private static final int EOF_MARKER = [0m[1;36m0x03[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m72[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m73[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m74[0m[39m:     * the parsed pfb-data.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m75[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:101[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m108[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException if an IO-error occurs.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:    public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:155[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m164[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:            int size = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record type: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, segment size: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, recordType, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:            long newTotal = total + size;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:101[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m108[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m101[0m[39m:     * @throws IOException if an IO-error occurs.[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m102[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m103[0m[39m:    public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m104[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m105[0m[39m:        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m106[0m[39m:        [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m107[0m[39m:    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m108[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:260[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m260[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m260[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Root Cause Analysis  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The compilation error “possible lossy conversion from long to int” arises [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbecause the new helper method  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m … [0m[1;39m}[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```  [0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     expects an `int` for `maxLength`, yet the class-level constant `MAX_LENGTH` is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdeclared as a `long` [0m[1;39m([0m[39m100_000_000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m. Passing a `long` into an `int` parameter is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39millegal without an explicit cast, and here an implicit cast would be lossy.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Core Insights & Preservation of Existing Logic  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The helper’s core job is to read up to `MAX_LENGTH` bytes in [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m KB chunks, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtallying bytes read and throwing an `IOException` if the running total exceeds the [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcap.  [0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All segment‐level checks in `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` already use `long total` and [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompare against `MAX_LENGTH` as `long`. We must preserve that behavior and [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsistency.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only the helper’s signature needs widening from `int` to `long`; the internal [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer logic and exceptions remain valid.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The constructor patch [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreplacing `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with the bounded read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msound and must be reapplied against the initial codebase.[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Step-by-Step Patch Outline  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Modify the helper method signature and its parameter type:  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Change  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        to  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, long maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Within the method, no other changes to logic are needed—`totalRead` remains[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39ma `long`, and you compare `totalRead > maxLength`.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Reapply the constructor replacement:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - In `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, replace  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        with  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This preserves the intended cap on initial read, preventing unbounded [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptional but recommended for completeness[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Prevent unbounded reads in the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfilename constructor:  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Change  [0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFiles.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        to  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream fis = [0m[1;35mFiles.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfis, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - This funnels *all* entry points through the same capped‐read logic.  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   D. No other code, harness, or tests need alteration; all existing behavior in [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`parsePfb` stays intact.[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Justification & Side-Effect Analysis  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Changing the helper signature to accept a `long` directly fixes the [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcompilation error without any loss of functionality or precision.  [0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing segment‐size checks compare `long newTotal` vs. `MAX_LENGTH` as a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`long`; this unified approach retains consistency.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The optional update to the filename‐based constructor closes a secondary [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39munbounded‐read loophole, but even if omitted, the primary fuzzer path [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstructor[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is now safe.  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No broad exception swallowing is introduced; OOM conditions become predictable[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException`s once the bound is hit.  [0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Tests and downstream consumers of `PfbParser` will see unchanged behavior for [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwell‐formed fonts under size limits, and controlled failures for oversized inputs.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Final Deliverables  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A single commit to `PfbParser.java` that:  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Adjusts the `readLimited` method signature to `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, long [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Replaces `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in the `InputStream` constructor with [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. [0m[1;39m([0m[39mOptionally[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Refactors the `String` constructor to use the same helper.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No modifications to harness, tests, or external libraries.  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This minimal, type-consistent patch resolves the compilation error and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39menforces the intended memory cap.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase experiences a Java heap space OutOfMemoryError when parsing large or [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmalformed PFB font data via the `PfbParser` class under fuzz testing. The initial [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39missue arises in `PfbParser.parsePfb` after reading the entire input into memory. [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe submitted patch replaces the unbounded `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` call with a custom [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`readLimited` method that enforces a `MAX_LENGTH` byte limit on the input. Despite [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthis change, the fuzzer still triggers an OOM in `parsePfb`, indicating that the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch did not eliminate the excessive memory use during parsing.[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Exception:  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of memory [0m[1;39m([0m[39muse [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m'-Xmx1710m'[0m[39m to reproduce[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     Caused by: java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace highlights:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - OOM thrown at [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     - `PfbParser` is invoked by `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, which is called by [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDType1Font.<init>`, then flows through PDFBox font factory and text stripper [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcode, ending in the user’s fuzzer harness.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Key observations  [0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The unbounded call `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` in `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` loads the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentire input into a byte array, directly contributing to heap overconsumption when [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minputs are large.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash reproduces reliably under fuzzing, indicating that no upstream [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mresource limits or early aborts occur before the heap is exhausted.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Patch attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A new private method was added:  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```java[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, long maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         ByteArrayOutputStream baos = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m buffer = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m8192[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         long totalRead = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         int n;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mn = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             totalRead += n;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotalRead > maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                 throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB font exceeds maximum allowed size: "[0m[39m + [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotalRead[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m             [0m[1;35mbaos.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuffer, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, n[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         return [0m[1;35mbaos.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor was updated to:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```diff[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -   public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     -       byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +   public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfinal InputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     +       byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m         [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     ```[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The byte-array constructor remains unchanged apart from formatting.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Result after patch  [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - A similar OutOfMemoryError still occurs, now at [0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:183[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline numbers shifted due to the patch[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshowing that limiting the initial read did not prevent large or complex structures [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin `parsePfb` from exhausting the heap.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The crash path remains the same: parsing in `PfbParser`, font creation in [0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m202[0m[39m:        lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = dstPos;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m203[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m204[0m[39m:        [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m copy the binary segments[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m205[0m[39m:        for [0m[1;39m([0m[39mint i = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m; i < [0m[1;35mtypeList.size[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; ++i[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m206[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m207[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mtypeList.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != BINARY_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m208[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m210[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m211[0m[39m:            byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ar = [0m[1;35mbarrList.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mi[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m212[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mSystem.arraycopy[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, pfbdata, dstPos, ar.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m213[0m[39m:            dstPos += ar.length;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m214[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m215[0m[39m:        lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m][0m[39m = dstPos - lengths[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m216[0m[39m:        [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
