[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m137[0m[39m:            int r = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m138[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mr == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m && total > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m139[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:171[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m175[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m171[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m172[0m[39m:            total += size;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m173[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mtypeList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m174[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mbarrList.add[0m[1;39m([0m[39mar[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m175[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:63[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m71[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m63[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m64[0m[39m:     * the EOF marker.[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m65[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m66[0m[39m:    private static final int EOF_MARKER = [0m[1;36m0x03[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m67[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m68[0m[39m:    [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m69[0m[39m:     * Heuristically chosen max length to buffer a Type1 font[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m70[0m[39m:     *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m71[0m[39m:    private static final long MAX_LENGTH = 100_000_000;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code>[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:155[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m164[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m155[0m[39m:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m156[0m[39m:            int size = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m157[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m158[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m159[0m[39m:            size += [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m160[0m[39m:            [0m[1;35mLOG.debug[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record type: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m, segment size: [0m[32m{[0m[32m}[0m[32m"[0m[39m, recordType, size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m161[0m[39m:            long newTotal = total + size;[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m162[0m[39m:            if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m163[0m[39m:                throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"record size would be too large: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m164[0m[39m:            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode[0m[39m>[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Reapply and retain the `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` patch in the [0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructor to bound the *total* PFB byte-array size. This[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprevents a single huge segment from exhausting the heap on initial read.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Introduce a new constant in `PfbParser.java` to bound the *number* of PFB [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegments:[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m around line [0m[1;36m70[0m[39m, alongside MAX_LENGTH[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[39m**[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    * Upper bound on the number of individual PFB segments [0m[1;39m([0m[39mASCII or binary[0m[1;39m)[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    * to prevent DoS via many tiny segments.[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    *[0m[35m/[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final int MAX_SEGMENTS = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. In the `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, declare and maintain a segment counter. [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mImmediately after reading the [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m-byte record marker and [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte size header [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore allocating each segment’s byte array[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, increment this counter and throw an [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` if it exceeds `MAX_SEGMENTS`. For example:[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int segmentCount = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   do [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int marker = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;     [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m should be [0m[1;36m0x80[0m[39m or EOF_MARKER[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mmarker == [0m[1;36m-1[0m[39m && total > [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m break; [0m[1;39m}[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int recordType = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m read size as before[0m[33m...[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       int size = [0m[33m...[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Enforce segment‐count cap before allocating:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       segmentCount++;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegmentCount > MAX_SEGMENTS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many PFB segments: "[0m[39m + segmentCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m existing size-check & byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m ar = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m; [0m[33m...[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m rest of loop unchanged[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mrecordType != EOF_MARKER[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Leave the rest of the `parsePfb` logic intact—including the two lists [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`typeList` and `barrList`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, the header-less concatenation into `pfbdata`, and [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msubsequent `[0m[1;35mgetSegment1[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[35m/[0m[95mgetSegment2[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` APIs—so that valid Type1/PFB fonts [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39malways use at most three segments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m are fully supported.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. No changes to harness, tests, or external libraries. The new exception on [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive segments will simply abort parsing early for malicious or fuzzed inputs, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mavoiding an uncontrolled accumulation of small arrays and preventing heap [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexhaustion under fuzz testing.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJustification:[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The original root cause is unbounded list growth and many small byte-array [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocations inside `parsePfb`, which the prior `MAX_LENGTH` check does not prevent [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhen an attacker uses many sub-segments whose sizes sum under the limit.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Bounding the number of segments to a few thousand [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m024[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m stops the DoS vector [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile still accommodating all legitimate PFB fonts [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhich normally have [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegments[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- All existing behavior for well-formed fonts is preserved: total input size is [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstill capped, segments are still parsed and concatenated correctly, and public APIs[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`getSegment1`, `getSegment2`, `size`, etc.[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m remain unchanged.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Potential side effect: extremely exotic or non-standard PFBs with hundreds of [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegments [0m[1;39m([0m[39munlikely in practice[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m will now be rejected with an `IOException`. If [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnecessary, the cap can be tuned upward, but [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m024[0m[39m is a safe default far above the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtypical three segments of a standard PFB.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/28/25 02:34:55][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.ANALYZE                  ]8;id=949501;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=134381;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue is a Java OutOfMemoryError raised during parsing of a PFB [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mPrinter Font Binary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m stream in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb`. A [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfuzzing harness triggered the failure via `PDFExtractTextFuzzer`, leading to a heap[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexhaustion at `PfbParser.parsePfb`.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch attempt introduced two new limits in `PfbParser`:  [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• A global byte‐count limit [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_LENGTH = [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[39m [0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m enforced by a new [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`readLimited` method that reads at most MAX_LENGTH bytes into memory.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m• A maximum segment count [0m[1;39m([0m[39mMAX_SEGMENTS = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m enforced in the segment‐parsing [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloop to prevent excessive splits.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the same OOM error still occurs in `parsePfb` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnow at [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mline [0m[1;36m195[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating the new guards did not prevent the uncontrolled allocation [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpath.[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Initial Issue  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Exception: `com.code_intelligence.jazzer.api.FuzzerSecurityIssueLow: Out of [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmemory [0m[1;39m([0m[39muse [0m[32m'-Xmx1710m'[0m[39m to reproduce[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Root exception: `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Java heap space`  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Stack trace highlights:  [0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Upstream calls through `Type1Font.createWithPFB`, [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFontFactory.createFont`, and the PDF text‐stripping engine in PDFBox.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Observations:  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • The entire PFB input stream is read unbounded, then passed to `parsePfb`, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich allocates buffers and concatenates segments.  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • A specially crafted or very large PFB payload drives heap usage beyond [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimits.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Patch Attempt  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added two constants in `PfbParser.java`:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `private static final long MAX_LENGTH = 100_000_000;`  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • `private static final int MAX_SEGMENTS = [0m[1;36m1024[0m[39m;`  [0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduced `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, long maxLength[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to read up to [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_LENGTH bytes, throwing `IOException` if exceeded.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Updated `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` to use `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` instead of `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - In the `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method:  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Introduced a `segmentCount` variable.  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Incremented and checked it against MAX_SEGMENTS on each segment.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Threw `IOException` if too many segments are encountered.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Post-Patch Result  [0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzing run still crashes with an OOM at:  [0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     `[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:195[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This shows that despite limiting raw input length and segment count, the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing logic in `parsePfb` can still trigger large or repeated allocations that [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexhaust the heap.[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Areas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The `parsePfb` method implementation in `org.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser`:  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • How buffers are allocated and grown when concatenating segments.  [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     • Any intermediate arrays or data structures that may exceed intended limits. [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The constructors and initial data‐stage in `PfbParser`, especially how [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`pfbdata` is sized and filled.  [0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Interactions between PFB parsing and higher‐level PDFBox classes [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`Type1Font`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`PDFType1Font`, `PDFontFactory`, and `PDFTextStripper`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, to see if additional [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffering or conversions happen after `parsePfb`.  [0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Configuration values for MAX_LENGTH and MAX_SEGMENTS, and whether they align [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith realistic font sizes or need tuning.  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The fuzzer harness entry point [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer.fuzzerTestOneInput`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconfirm that only font parsing—and not unrelated code paths—is driving the OOM.[0m     [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo eliminate the OOM in PfbParser.parsePfb while preserving existing functionality [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand fuzzing harnesses, we will&nbsp;reapply and extend the last patch as follows:[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Centralize and enforce MAX_LENGTH on all entry‐points  [0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1.1[0m[39m. Remove any unconstrained reads.  [0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Replace both  [0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; … [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`  [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   • `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m[39m [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mFiles.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m; [0m[1;39m}[0m[39m`  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   with calls into our new `[0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m1.2[0m[39m. Add a guard in the byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m constructor:  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m bytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws IOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes.length > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB font exceeds maximum allowed size: "[0m[39m + [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbytes.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m     [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Result: No matter how you invoke PfbParser, the raw bytes can never exceed [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_LENGTH.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Harden [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to prevent integer‐overflow and excess segments  [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2.1[0m[39m. Interpret the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m‐byte segment length as unsigned.  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint b0 = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint b1 = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint b2 = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint b3 = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb0|b1|b2|b3[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m < [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mEOFException[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m unsigned [0m[1;36m32[0m[39m‐bit size[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlong size = [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb0 & [0m[1;36m0xFF[0m[39mL[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb1 & [0m[1;36m0xFF[0m[39mL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m8[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb2 & [0m[1;36m0xFF[0m[39mL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m16[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m          | [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mb3 & [0m[1;36m0xFF[0m[39mL[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m << [0m[1;36m24[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2.2[0m[39m. Before you allocate or read that many bytes, enforce:  [0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegmentCount++;[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39msegmentCount > MAX_SEGMENTS[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Too many PFB segments: "[0m[39m + segmentCount[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || size > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Invalid segment size: "[0m[39m + size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal += size;[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Total PFB size would exceed limit: "[0m[39m + total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2.3[0m[39m. Read the segment data into a new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m of `[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39msize`.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m2.4[0m[39m. Keep lists of segment‐types + byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m for concatenation.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Before concatenating segments, final size guard + drop original raw bytes  [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3.1[0m[39m. Right before `pfbdata = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m([0m[39mint[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m total[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;`, assert:  [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m should never happen given the loop checks, but double‐check:[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Total buffer size would exceed MAX_LENGTH: "[0m[39m + total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;36m3.2[0m[39m. Null out the original `byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb` reference [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthe input to parsePfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   – this allows the GC to reclaim that array before allocating pfbdata.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Summary of Memory Profile After Patch  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Raw bytes: up to MAX_LENGTH  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Per‐segment arrays: total bytes = MAX_LENGTH [0m[1;39m([0m[39mbut released as soon as [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconcatenation finishes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m  [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  • Final pfbdata: up to MAX_LENGTH  [0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  Peak working set ≈ [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m× MAX_LENGTH instead of unbounded. With a [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB cap, typical[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheaps [0m[1;39m([0m[39m≥[0m[1;36m300[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m easily accommodate this.  [0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Why This Fix  [0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  A. Closes the bypass in the file‐and‐byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m constructors that once used [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`readAllBytes` or `Files.readAllBytes`.  [0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  B. Stops integer‐overflow in segment‐size computation by masking to unsigned.  [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  C. Prevents “low‐size” repeated segments DoS via a MAX_SEGMENTS guard.  [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  D. Guards total concatenation size twice: during loop and just before final [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation.  [0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  E. Retains existing APIs, existing tests, and does not touch harness or fuzz [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlogic.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPotential Side-Effects & Mitigations  [0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – Legitimately large PFB fonts >[0m[1;36m100[0m[39m MB will now throw IOException [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlow risk—Type [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m fonts are almost always <[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m MB[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  – By nulling the input array reference before the final allocation, we rely on [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe GC to free memory; however, GC scheduling is out of our control. In practice, [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe VM frees contiguous arrays quickly when required.  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mReferences in Codebase  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m • We already introduced `private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadLimited[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream, long[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m • `PDFJetParser` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot real[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but analogous classes follow a two‐pass parse with [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtotal‐size checks.  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m • Similar pattern in `[0m[1;35mPDDocument.load[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` enforces file size limits before full [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffering.  [0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––––[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m–––––––––––––––––––––––––  [0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java: [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mninety-to-hundred-and-twenty<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java: [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mone-hundred-fifty-to-two-hundred-and-ten<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java: [0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mforty-to-sixty<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>  [0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m# Evaluation Report[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe codebase exhibits an out-of-memory failure when parsing large or malformed PFB [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfont data through `PfbParser.parsePfb`. A proposed patch adds a check against a [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_LENGTH` threshold before allocating the combined buffer [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfbdata`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrowing an `IOException` if the total byte count would exceed the limit. After [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mapplying this check, the same `OutOfMemoryError` in `PfbParser.parsePfb` still [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moccurs, indicating the guard does not prevent all excessive memory allocations.[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mInitial Issue  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- A fuzzing run on PDF text extraction [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PDFExtractTextFuzzer`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m triggers a Java [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap space exhaustion at [0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35morg.apache.fontbox.pfb.PfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mPfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace shows the error propagating from font parsing [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`PfbParser` → [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`Type1Font.createWithPFB` → `PDType1Font` → PDFBox text stripper[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The failure is classified as a low-severity security issue [0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39m`FuzzerSecurityIssueLow`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m but indicates an unbounded memory allocation risk when [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mreading PFB font segments.[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mPatch Attempt  [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- In `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`, immediately [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbefore `pfbdata = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mtotal[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;`, the patch inserts:  [0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m enforce overall size limit before allocating final buffer[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Total PFB size would exceed limit: "[0m[39m + total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m  ```  [0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This check was intended to prevent creating an overly large byte array by [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomparing the cumulative segment size [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`total`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m against a predefined `MAX_LENGTH`.[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mResult After Patch  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- After recompiling with the added size check, the same `OutOfMemoryError: Java [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mheap space` occurs at `PfbParser.parsePfb` [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating the guard did not[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger in this crash scenario.  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The stack trace remains identical, revealing that either `total` does not exceed [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`MAX_LENGTH` for this input case or the allocation elsewhere still grows too large.[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAreas for Further Investigation  [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The logic that computes `total` in `PfbParser.parsePfb` [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., per-segment length[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalculations and summations[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.  [0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The definitions and value of `MAX_LENGTH`—whether it aligns with realistic memory[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstraints.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Other code paths in `PfbParser` that allocate buffers [0m[1;39m([0m[39mintermediate binary [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msegments, clear-to-mark buffers[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m outside the guarded allocation.  [0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Any fontbox utilities that read or expand segments before the `total` check, to [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msee if they create large temporary arrays.  [0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Downstream consumers in PDFBox [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., `PDFontFactory`, `PDType1Font`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m that might [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtrigger additional allocations based on parsed data.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Interaction with the fuzzer harness [0m[1;39m([0m[39meven though it is not the root cause[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdetermine how inputs are constructed and whether they can bypass `MAX_LENGTH` [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mchecks.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
