[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Overview of Root Causes[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Unbounded `[0m[1;35mreadAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls in `[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` and [0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` constructors allocate the entire PFB payload up front, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mleading to OOM before any guard executes.[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Although there is a cumulative `MAX_LENGTH` check in `parsePfb`, it only fires[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter reading each segment’s length and before summing into `total`. It does not:[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Prevent the initial `pfb` array from exceeding `MAX_LENGTH`.  [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       • Prevent allocation of a single segment byte array [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m when [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`size` itself is very large [0m[1;39m([0m[39meven if `total + size <= MAX_LENGTH`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The final buffer allocation `new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mtotal[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` is already guarded but [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minsufficient alone.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Logical Constraints to Preserve[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Existing successful parsing paths for well-formed, reasonably sized PFBs must [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mremain unaffected.[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All pre-existing error semantics [0m[1;39m([0m[39mthrowing `IOException` on malformed or [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtruncated PFBs[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m should be retained.[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No changes to fuzz harnesses, external utilities, or dependencies.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maintain the same `MAX_LENGTH` constant and its semantic meaning as an overall[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcap.[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Proposed Multi-Point Patch Strategy[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   A. Replace unbounded reads with a bounded-read utility  [0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Introduce a private helper method within `PfbParser.java`:  [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        private static byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m [0m[1;35mreadUpTo[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in, int maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throws [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            ByteArrayOutputStream out = new [0m[1;35mByteArrayOutputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m buf = new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;36m8192[0m[1;39m][0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            int read, total = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            while [0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m([0m[39mread = [0m[1;35min.read[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m != [0m[1;36m-1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                total += read;[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtotal > maxBytes[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB input exceeds maximum allowed size: [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m"[0m[39m + total[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                [0m[1;35mout.write[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbuf, [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m, read[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            return [0m[1;35mout.toByteArray[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Modify constructors:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mString filename[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – Replace `[0m[1;35mFiles.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with:[0m               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              ```java[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              try [0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream fis = [0m[1;35mFiles.newInputStream[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mPaths.get[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfilename[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                  [0m[1;35mthis[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mreadUpTo[0m[1;39m([0m[39mfis, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              ```[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        - `public [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream in[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`  [0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            – Replace `[0m[1;35min.readAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` with:[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              ```java[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb = [0m[1;35mreadUpTo[0m[1;39m([0m[39min, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m              ```[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This prevents any initial allocation larger than `MAX_LENGTH + small buffer`,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrowing early.[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   B. Early guard on the input byte array  [0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • At the start of `[0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`, insert:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpfb.length > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB input exceeds maximum allowed size: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpfb.length[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      This defends against direct `new [0m[1;35mPfbParser[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` calls with oversized [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39marrays.[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   C. Strengthen per-segment allocation checks  [0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • After reading the [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m-byte `size` value, before allocating `new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madd:[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize < [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m || size > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"PFB segment size invalid or too large: "[0m[39m + [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msize[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      • Retain the cumulative check:[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```java[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        long newTotal = total + size;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnewTotal > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Cumulative PFB size would exceed limit: "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mnewTotal[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        ```[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Implementation Steps[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. Open `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.java`.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. Define the `[0m[1;35mreadUpTo[0m[1;39m([0m[39mInputStream,int[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` helper near the top of the class.[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. In the `String` and `InputStream` constructors, swap out `[0m[1;35mreadAllBytes[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwith calls to `[0m[1;35mreadUpTo[0m[1;39m([0m[33m...[0m[39m, MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. In `private void [0m[1;35mparsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[1;39m][0m[39m pfb[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround lines [0m[1;36m124[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m132[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert the [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mearly length guard.[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m. In the loop that reads each segment [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines ~[0m[1;36m155[0m[39m–[0m[1;36m164[0m[39m and the subsequent [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mallocation at ~[0m[1;36m166[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, insert:[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - `if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msize > MAX_LENGTH[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m throw [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"...: "[0m[39m + size[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m      - Ensure both `size` and `newTotal` guards are in place before any `new [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbyte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39msize[0m[1;39m][0m[39m`.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;36m6[0m[39m. Keep the final `new byte[0m[1;39m[[0m[39mtotal[0m[1;39m][0m[39m` allocation and its existing guard intact.[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Justification and Benefits[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - By capping the initial read, we eliminate the possibility of allocating the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mentire input into memory if it exceeds `MAX_LENGTH`.  [0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Per-segment bounds prevent a single large segment from causing OOM, even if [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe cumulative size remains valid.  [0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - The early guard in `parsePfb` ensures any direct byte-array inputs are also [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconstrained.  [0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing parsing logic, error detection for malformed markers, and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdownstream consumers remain unchanged for bona fide PFB files.  [0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Exceptions for oversize inputs are thrown promptly, returning controlled [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`IOException` errors instead of unhandled `OutOfMemoryError`.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. Side-Effect Mitigation[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate PFB files slightly above `MAX_LENGTH` will now yield an [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException; ensure `MAX_LENGTH` is chosen high enough to accommodate real-world [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfonts.  [0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Performance overhead of the bounded read helper is minimal [0m[1;39m([0m[39mchunked reads[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39monly applies when the input is large.[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. Code Ranges for Patch Context[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:90[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m118[0m[39m<[0m[35m/[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:124[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m132[0m[39m<[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   <code_range>fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/pfb/PfbParser.jav[0m[1;92ma:155[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m173[0m[39m<[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[95mcode_range[0m[39m>[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m[12/28/25 02:43:51][0m[2;36m [0m[34mINFO    [0m Prism Supervisor Routing: TeamStatus.EVALUATE -> TeamStatus.END                      ]8;id=890633;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py\[2m__init__.py[0m]8;;\[2m:[0m]8;id=145694;file:///home/qqor/crete/packages/crete/framework/agent/services/prism/__init__.py#160\[2m160[0m]8;;\

[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/home/qqor/crete/packages/python_oss_fuzz/.oss_fuzz/build/out/[0m[95mpdfbox[0m                 [2m               [0m
